          <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Back at Christie=E2=
=80=99s for the final evening sale of the cycle, I wasn=E2=80=99t expecting=
 much. After all, the week seemed to be mostly about exceptional works, and=
 there were few =E2=80=9Cmasterpieces=E2=80=9D in this sale.<br/><br/>Still=
, there was the <b>David Hammons</b> Flight Fantasy work that was priced at=
 $2 million and got bid to $3.2 million by several women in the room. <b>Ce=
cily Brown</b>=E2=80=99s <i>The Butcher and the Policeman</i>, from 2013, h=
ardly qualifies as a masterpiece within her body of work. As I heard one pe=
rson say, =E2=80=9CThere are so many other things to spend $4 million on.=
=E2=80=9D But that didn=E2=80=99t stop bidders=E2=80=94including some art a=
dvisors who traffic in Brown=E2=80=99s work=E2=80=94from pushing the painti=
ng to a $4.9 million hammer, $5.97 million with fees. Brown now has 10 work=
s that have sold at auction for between $5.8 million and $6.7 million, all =
in the
past six years. It=E2=80=99s a tight band for her top auction prices. <br/>=
<br/><b>Rudolf Stingel</b> also finally found some market footing at Christ=
ie=E2=80=99s. His self-portrait, from 2007, was estimated at $1.8 million, =
but sold to the third-party guarantor for a $1.7 million hammer. That might=
 sound disappointing, but the Stingel market has been disorganized for year=
s, a victim of several converging forces including the fraudster <b>Inigo P=
hilbrick</b>=E2=80=99s heavy trafficking in the artist. Still, the last lot=
 in Christie=E2=80=99s sale was another Stingel, a carpet painting from 201=
0, that had been owned by the great collector <b>Rosa de la Cruz</b>. The b=
uyer paid $945,000, solidly above the $600,000 estimate, which was supporte=
d by a third-party guarantee. When I spoke to the buyer=E2=80=99s advisor, =
who was the one bidding in the room, the advisor shrugged and defended the =
purchase by saying, =E2=80=9CHe=E2=80=99s a great artist=E2=80=94and the pr=
ices are finally down to where they should be.=E2=80=9D<br/></td>
         </tr>
